query:
SELECT 
  p.apiId,
  a.name as apiName,
  p.serviceId,
  s.name as serviceName,
  s.smshubCode,
  p.countryId,
  c.name as countryName,
  p.ourPrice as price,
  p.quantityAvailable as available,
  a.priority
FROM prices p
INNER JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
INNER JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
INNER JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
WHERE p.serviceId = (SELECT id FROM services WHERE smshubCode = 'wa' LIMIT 1)
  AND p.countryId = 1
  AND p.apiId IS NOT NULL
  AND a.active = 1
ORDER BY a.priority
